122875490.AbilityDescription:
FL4K sends forward 2 [actionskill]Rakk[/actionskill] to dive-bomb enemies.

This skill has multiple charges.

2811446764.AbilityDescription:
FL4K [actionskill]cloaks[/actionskill], turning invisible. FL4K can fire 3 shots while [actionskill]cloaked[/actionskill], and each shot is automatically a [skillbold]Critical Hit[/skillbold].

While [actionskill]cloaked[/actionskill], FL4K has increased [skillbold]Movement Speed[/skillbold] and [skillbold]Health Regeneration[/skillbold].

3114692079.AbilityDescription:
FL4K creates a [actionskill]Rift[/actionskill] at a target location, teleporting their pet through the [actionskill]Rift[/actionskill] and dealing [skillbold]Radiation Damage[/skillbold] to nearby enemies.

Additionally, FL4K’s pet becomes irradiated, growing in size and dealing bonus [skillbold]Radiation Damage[/skillbold] when it attacks.

Using [actionskill]Gamma Burst[/actionskill] while FL4K’s Pet is downed or dead will [skillbold]revive[/skillbold] the pet at the targeted location with 30% of its health, but will double [skillbold]Action Skill Cooldown Time[/skillbold].

1673352944.Description:
FL4K's [actionskill]Spiderant[/actionskill] evolves into a [actionskill]Scorcher[/actionskill], occasionally dealing Incendiary Damage to all enemies nearby. While accompanied by the [actionskill]Scorcher[/actionskill], FL4K constantly [skillbold]regenerates health[/skillbold] and gains [skillbold]Elemental Resistance[/skillbold].

When FL4K issues an [skillbold]Attack Command[/skillbold], the [actionskill]Scorcher[/actionskill] will charge enemies.

1876473248.Description:
FL4K is joined by a loyal [Actionskill]Skag[/Actionskill] companion, which will increase FL4K's [skillbold]Damage[/skillbold].

Hold {OakPC_ActionSkill} to issue an [skillbold]Attack Command[/skillbold], which will cause the [Actionskill]Skag[/Actionskill] to vomit acid onto enemies.

1899745313.Description:
FL4K’s [actionskill]Skag[/actionskill] evolves into an [actionskill]Eridian Skag[/actionskill], which will increase FL4K’s [skillbold]Damage[/skillbold] and [skillbold]Fire Rate[/skillbold].

When FL4K issues an [skillbold]Attack Command[/skillbold], their [actionskill]Eridian Skag[/actionskill] pulls nearby enemies in by generating a [skillbold]Singularity[/skillbold].

2041327099.Description: While [actionskill]Gamma Burst[/actionskill] is active, FL4K’s pet is surrounded by a [skillbold]Radiation Aura[/skillbold], constantly damaging all nearby enemies.

2329546787.Description:
FL4K’s [actionskill]Jabber[/actionskill] upgrades his gear and equips an [skillbold]SMG[/skillbold]. While accompanied by the [actionskill]Gunslinger[/actionskill], FL4K gains increased [skillbold]Movement Speed[/skillbold] and [skillbold]Critical Hit Damage[/skillbold].

When FL4K issues an [skillbold]Attack Command[/skillbold], the [actionskill]Gunslinger[/actionskill] equips a [skillbold]Rocket Launcher[/skillbold] to attack the target.

2492363046.Description:
FL4K’s [actionskill]Spiderant[/actionskill] evolves into a [actionskill]Countess[/actionskill], which will cause FL4K to constantly [skillbold]regenerate health[/skillbold] and gain [skillbold]Damage Reduction[/skillbold].

When FL4K issues an [skillbold]Attack Command[/skillbold], the [actionskill]Countess[/actionskill] will burrow underground and then emerge dealing [skillbold]Corrosive Damage[/skillbold] in an area.

2685588938.Description:
FL4K is joined by a loyal [actionskill]Spiderant[/actionskill] companion, which will cause FL4K to constantly [skillbold]regenerate health[/skillbold].

Hold {OakPC_ActionSkill} to issue an [skillbold]Attack Command[/skillbold], which will cause the [Actionskill]Spiderant[/Actionskill] to charge into enemies.

2701689408.Description: When FL4K or FL4K’s [actionskill]Pet[/actionskill] kills an enemy while [actionskill]Gamma Burst[/actionskill] is active, the duration of [actionskill]Gamma Burst[/actionskill] is extended and pet damage is increased. These effects can stack up to 5 times.

2703933108.Description: The [skillbold]Health Regeneration[/skillbold] and [skillbold]Movement Speed[/skillbold] of [actionskill]Fade Away[/actionskill] persists for a short time after the skill has ended.

2744910560.Description: Successive hits on the same target increase FL4K's [skillbold]Critical Damage[/skillbold] per hit. [skillbold]Unblinking Eye[/skillbold] resets every 3 hits.

2841879906.Description:
FL4K’s [Actionskill]Skag[/Actionskill] evolves into a larger, [Actionskill]Great Horned Skag[/Actionskill] which will increase FL4K’s [skillbold]Damage[/skillbold] and [skillbold]Gun Damage[/skillbold].

When FL4K issues an [skillbold]Attack Command[/skillbold], the Great Horned Skag will charge at enemies and knock them into the air.

2842141809.Description: After using [actionskill]Gamma Burst[/actionskill], the [actionskill]Rift[/actionskill] remains for the duration of the skill. While standing near the [actionskill]Rift[/actionskill], FL4K and their allies rapidly [skillbold]Regenerate Health[/skillbold].

325197786.Description: When FL4K’s [actionskill]Rakk[/actionskill] damage an enemy, a portion of FL4K’s health is [skillbold]restored[/skillbold].

345989920.Description: For the duration of [actionskill]Gamma Burst[/actionskill], [skillbold]Damage[/skillbold] dealt by FL4K is increased.

3490486612.Description:
After [actionskill]Fade Away[/actionskill] ends, FL4K’s pet will [skillbold]Taunt[/skillbold], drawing the attention of all enemies in a huge radius.

For a few seconds after [skillbold]Taunting[/skillbold], the pet gains powerful [skillbold]Damage Reduction[/skillbold].

3793471331.Description:
FL4K is joined by a loyal [actionskill]Jabber[/actionskill] companion, armed with a [skillbold]Pistol[/skillbold]. While accompanied by the [actionskill]Jabber[/actionskill], FL4K’s [skillbold]Movement Speed[/skillbold] is increased.

Hold {OakPC_ActionSkill} to issue an [skillbold]Attack Command[/skillbold], which will cause the [Actionskill]Jabber[/Actionskill] to throw a [skillbold]Radiation Barrel[/skillbold] at enemies.

390492389.Description: When FL4K’s [actionskill]pet[/actionskill] is at low health, it gains [skillbold]Damage Reduction[/skillbold] and [skillbold]regenerates health[/skillbold]. This skill has a long cooldown.

4171864922.Description: When FL4K is in [skillbold]Fight For Your Life[/skillbold], their [actionskill]pet[/actionskill] will attempt to [skillbold]revive[/skillbold] them.

43942644.Description:
FL4K’s [Actionskill]Jabber[/Actionskill] evolves into a [Actionskill]Beefcake[/Actionskill], discarding its pistol and equipping a [skillbold]Shotgun[/skillbold]. While accompanied by the [Actionskill]Beefcake[/Actionskill], FL4K gains increased [skillbold]Movement Speed[/skillbold] and [skillbold]Maximum Health[/skillbold].

When FL4K issues an [skillbold]Attack Command[/skillbold], the [Actionskill]Beefcake[/Actionskill] will summon a melee weapon to deliver a powerful attack that [skillbold]knocks enemies back[/skillbold].

447597971.Description: [actionskill]Fade Away[/actionskill] no longer ends after FL4K attacks, at the cost of [skillbold]Critical Hit Damage[/skillbold] and [actionskill]Fade Away[/actionskill] duration being reduced.

1292218990.FlavorText: [skillflavor]The eyes are the groin of the face.[/skillflavor]

1127977552.AbilityDescription: When FL4K scores a [skillbold]Critical Hit[/skillbold], there is a chance for 1 ammo to be added to their magazine.

117127705.AbilityDescription:
[skillbold]Hunter Skill[/skillbold]. After shooting an enemy, FL4K gains a stack of [skillbold]Furious Attack[/skillbold].

For each stack of [skillbold]Furious Attack[/skillbold], FL4K’s [skillbold]Handling[/skillbold] and [skillbold]Gun Damage[/skillbold] are increased. Stacks decay after a few seconds.

1401085196.AbilityDescription:

1474023286.AbilityDescription: While above half health, FL4K's [skillbold]Gun Damage[/skillbold] and [skillbold]Movement Speed[/skillbold] are increased.

1546991626.AbilityDescription: FL4K has a chance to fire an [skillbold]extra projectile[/skillbold] per shot.

202840317.AbilityDescription: When FL4K’s [actionskill]pet[/actionskill] attacks an enemy, the first melee attack is an automatic [skillbold]Critical Hit[/skillbold] that deals increased damage.

2030200031.AbilityDescription:
FL4K and FL4K’s [actionskill]Pet[/actionskill] gain increased [skillbold]Damage[/skillbold] when FL4K activates an Action Skill.

If FL4K is at [skillbold]full health[/skillbold], the increased [skillbold]Damage[/skillbold] is doubled.

2158073648.AbilityDescription: FL4K’s [skillbold]Maximum Health[/skillbold] is increased, and they constantly [skillbold]regenerate health[/skillbold].

2555484897.AbilityDescription: [skillbold]Hunter Skill[/skillbold]. When FL4K’s pet deals damage, FL4K and their pet gain a stack of [skillbold]Frenzy[/skillbold]. Each stack of [skillbold]Frenzy[/skillbold] increases [skillbold]Damage[/skillbold]. The stacks decay after a few seconds.

2581189346.AbilityDescription: While FL4K is at low health, a portion of all damage they take is [skillbold]shared[/skillbold] to their [actionskill]pet[/actionskill] instead.

2675403350.AbilityDescription: Increases FL4K’s [skillbold]Gun Damage[/skillbold] and [skillbold]Action Skill Duration[/skillbold].

2694263575.AbilityDescription:
All [skillbold]Damage[/skillbold] dealt by FL4K and their [actionskill]Pet[/actionskill] is increased.

281565876.AbilityDescription:

2927115417.AbilityDescription:

3320005682.AbilityDescription: FL4K gains [skillbold]bonuses[/skillbold] when fighting different types of enemies.

3579448174.AbilityDescription:
[skillbold]Hunter Kill Skill[/skillbold]. Whenever FL4K kills an enemy, they gain a stack of [skillbold]Interplanetary Stalker[/skillbold]. For each stack of [skillbold]Interplanetary Stalker[/skillbold], they gain a bonus to all damage dealt.

37164101.AbilityDescription: When FL4K takes damage, a portion of all damage they take is [skillbold]shared[/skillbold] to their [actionskill]pet[/actionskill] instead.

4206164656.AbilityDescription: FL4K gains increased [skillbold]Gun Damage[/skillbold] and [skillbold]Action Skill Damage[/skillbold].

Amara summons a giant fist that bursts from the ground and [skillbold]locks[/skillbold] the targeted enemy in place for a few seconds.

Amara summons a giant fist that bursts from the ground and [skillbold]locks[/skillbold] the targeted enemy in place for a few seconds.

Amara summons a giant fist that bursts from the ground and [skillbold]locks[/skillbold] the targeted enemy in place for a few seconds.

335451024.AbilityDescription: Whenever Amara applies a [skillbold]Status Effect[/skillbold] to an enemy, it has a chance to [skillbold]spread[/skillbold] to a nearby enemy.

Amara gains increased [skillbold]Melee Damage[/skillbold].

3740788879.AbilityDescription:

If a [skillbold]Blitz[/skillbold] melee attack kills an enemy, [skillbold]Blitz’s[/skillbold] cooldown is [skillbold]immediately reset[/skillbold].

4223438069.AbilityDescription: All [actionskill]Action Skill Augments[/actionskill] gain increased effects.

Amara's [actionskill]Action Skill[/actionskill] can be activated while it's [skillbold]cooling down[/skillbold]. This skill may only be used once per completed cooldown.

466974429.AbilityDescription: Amara deals increased [skillbold]Elemental Damage[/skillbold]. [skillbold]Shock damage[/skillbold] is further increased.

69544143.AbilityDescription: Amara's [skillbold]Status Effects[/skillbold] deal increased damage over time and have increased duration. Her [skillbold]Action Skill Status Effect[/skillbold] deals further increased damage.
